                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A ypotryll\u2019s charge shakes the ground it crosses. The path of its charge is considered difficult terrain until the start of the ypotryll\u2019s next turn, and creatures with tremorsense that are within 100 feet of the end of the ypotryll\u2019s charge are blinded for that same amount of time."
