                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "name": "Unstoppable Force",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A ypotryll\u2019s bonus on a charge attack is +4, and it may add this bonus on overrun combat maneuver checks attempted using Charge Through. A ypotryll may charge over difficult terrain, provided the terrain does not cost more than 2 squares to enter."
